<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">周颂·丝衣</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonca87770b757f">
丝衣其紑，载弁俅俅。自堂徂基，自羊徂牛，鼐鼎及鼒，兕觥其觩。旨酒思柔。不吴不敖，胡考之休。
</div>
</div>
